<STAGEDIR>Aside</STAGEDIR>Thissupernaturalsoliciting
Cannotbeill,cannotbegood:ifill,
Whyhathitgivenmeearnestofsuccess,
Commencinginatruth?IamthaneofCawdor:
Ifgood,whydoIyieldtothatsuggestion
Whosehorridimagedothunfixmyhair
Andmakemyseatedheartknockatmyribs,
Againsttheuseofnature?Presentfears
Arelessthanhorribleimaginings:
Mythought,whosemurderyetisbutfantastical,
Shakessomysinglestateofmanthatfunction
Issmother'dinsurmise,andnothingis
Butwhatisnot.
Look,howourpartner'srapt.
