Anabsolutetrust.
Oworthiestcousin!
Thesinofmyingratitudeevennow
Washeavyonme:thouartsofarbefore
Thatswiftestwingofrecompenseisslow
Toovertakethee.Wouldthouhadstlessdeserved,
Thattheproportionbothofthanksandpayment
Mighthavebeenmine!onlyIhavelefttosay,
Moreisthyduethanmorethanallcanpay.
TheserviceandtheloyaltyIowe,
Indoingit,paysitself.Yourhighness'part
Istoreceiveourduties;andourduties
Aretoyourthroneandstatechildrenandservants,
Whichdobutwhattheyshould,bydoingeverything
Safetowardyourloveandhonour.
