MyworthyCawdor!
<STAGEDIR>Aside</STAGEDIR>ThePrinceofCumberland!thatisastep
OnwhichImustfalldown,orelseo'erleap,
Forinmywayitlies.Stars,hideyourfires;
Letnotlightseemyblackanddeepdesires:
Theeyewinkatthehand;yetletthatbe,
Whichtheeyefears,whenitisdone,tosee.
True,worthyBanquo;heisfullsovaliant,
AndinhiscommendationsIamfed;
Itisabanquettome.Let'safterhim,
Whosecareisgonebeforetobiduswelcome:
Itisapeerlesskinsman.
'Theymetmeinthedayofsuccess:andIhave
