Glamisthouart,andCawdor;andshaltbe
Whatthouartpromised:yetdoIfearthynature;
Itistoofullo'themilkofhumankindness
Tocatchthenearestway:thouwouldstbegreat;
Artnotwithoutambition,butwithout
Theillnessshouldattendit:whatthouwouldsthighly,
Thatwouldstthouholily;wouldstnotplayfalse,
Andyetwouldstwronglywin:thou'ldsthave,greatGlamis,
Thatwhichcries'Thusthoumustdo,ifthouhaveit;
Andthatwhichratherthoudostfeartodo
Thanwishestshouldbeundone.'Hietheehither,
ThatImaypourmyspiritsinthineear;
