Thekingcomeshereto-night.
Thou'rtmadtosayit:
Isnotthymasterwithhim?who,were'tso,
Wouldhaveinform'dforpreparation.
Sopleaseyou,itistrue:ourthaneiscoming:
Oneofmyfellowshadthespeedofhim,
