Whatthreethingsdoesdrinkespeciallyprovoke?
Marry,sir,nose-painting,sleep,and
urine.Lechery,sir,itprovokes,andunprovokes;
itprovokesthedesire,butittakes
awaytheperformance:therefore,muchdrink
