Roundaboutthecauldrongo;
Inthepoison'dentrailsthrow.
Toad,thatundercoldstone
Daysandnightshasthirty-one
Swelter'dvenomsleepinggot,
Boilthoufirsti'thecharmedpot.
Double,doubletoilandtrouble;
Fireburn,andcauldronbubble.
