He'sworthnomore
Theysayhepartedwell,andpaidhisscore:
Andso,Godbewithhim!Herecomesnewercomfort.
Hail,king!forsothouart:behold,wherestands
Theusurper'scursedhead:thetimeisfree:
Iseetheecompass'dwiththykingdom'spearl,
